proc newMimetypes(): MimeDB {...}{.raises: [], tags: [].}
Creates a new Mimetypes database. The database will contain the most common mimetypes.   Source Edit 
proc getMimetype(mimedb: MimeDB; ext: string; default = "text/plain"): string {...}{.
    raises: [], tags: [].}
Gets mimetype which corresponds to ext. Returns default if ext could not be found. ext can start with an optional dot which is ignored.   Source Edit 
proc getExt(mimedb: MimeDB; mimetype: string; default = "txt"): string {...}{.raises: [],
    tags: [].}
Gets extension which corresponds to mimetype. Returns default if mimetype could not be found. Extensions are returned without the leading dot.   Source Edit
